<sentence ID="SENT-3" start="108" end="160"><ENAMEX TYPE="PER">2Slick</ENAMEX> pointed me to a article at In <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Iraq</ENAMEX> For 365 .</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-4" start="160" end="227">This is a great
