<sentence ID="SENT-8" start="574" end="770">Recalling the medical classes they&apos;d received from the special
forces, the Iraqis reacted calmly, fastening a belt above the wound,
creating a tourniquet, which stopped the gushing stream of red.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-9" start="770" end="839">They
<Event TYPE="Movement" SUBTYPE="Transport">moved</Event> the soldier to a <ENAMEX TYPE="VEH">MEDVAC</ENAMEX> vehicle via two-man litter carry.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-10" start="839" end="1034">After
