Iraq--every day . . . a lot of them aren&apos;t living in the <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">Green Zone</ENAMEX>,
they&apos;ve got to <Event TYPE="Movement" SUBTYPE="Transport">travel</Event> in from outside.</sentence> <sentence ID="SENT-24" start="2957" end="3105">They do not know at any point in
